Meshes of 22 MALEVNC tracts.

Source: R/data.R
MANC.tracts.Rd

MANC.tracts contains mesh of 22 MANC tracts in non-symmetric space: CVL_L, CVL_R, DLT_L, DLT_R, DLV_L, DLV_R, DMT_L, DMT_R, ITD_L, ITD_R, MDA_L, MDA_R, type-I_MTD_L, type-I_MTD_R, type-II_MTD_L, type-II_MTD_R, type-III_MTD_L, type-III_MTD_R, VLT_L, VLT_R, VTV_L, VTV_R

Usage

MANC.tracts

Format

An object of class hxsurf (inherits from list) of length 4.

Examples

if (FALSE) {
# Depends on nat
library(nat)
plot3d(MANC.tracts)
}
